quran[6{c,v,t}:
2,197,hajj ke mahinay ( Moueen hain jo ) maloom hain to shakhs un mahino mein hajj ki niyat karle to hajj ( ke dinon ) mein nah aurton se ikhtilaat kere nah koi bura kaam kere nah kisi se jhagrre. aur jo naik kaam tum karo ge woh khuda ko maloom hojaye ga aur zaad raah ( yani raste ka kharch ) sath le jao kyunkay behtar ( faida ) zaad raah ( ka ) parhaiz gari hai aur ae ahal aqal mujh se drtay raho
2,198,is ka tumhe kuch gunah nahi ke ( hajj ke dinon mein ba zarea tijarat ) apne perwar-digaar se rozi talab karo aur jab Arfat se wapas honay lagu to Musher haraam ( yani mazdulfay ) mein khuda ka zikar karo aur is terhan zikar karo jis terhan is ne tum ko sikhaya. aur is se peshtar tum log ( un tareeqon se ) mehez nawaqif they
2,199,phir jahan se aur log wapas hon wahein se tum bhi wapas ho aur khuda se bakhshish mango. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala aur rehmat karne wala hai
2,200,phir jab hajj ke tamam arkaan poooray kar chuko to ( money mein ) khuda ko yaad karo. jis terhan apne baap dada ko yaadkiya karte they balkay is se bhi ziyada aur baaz log aisay hain jo ( khuda se ) iltija karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko ( jo duniya hai ) duniya hi mein inayat kar aisay logon ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi
2,201,aur baze aisay hain ke dua karte hain ke perwar-digaar hum ko duniya mein bhi Nemat ataa farma aur akhirat mein bhi Nemat bakhshiyon aur dozakh ke azaab se mehfooz rakiyo
2,202,yahi log hain jin ke liye un ke kamon ka hissa ( yani ajar naik tayyar ) hai aur khuda jald hisaab lainay wala ( aur jald ajar dainay wala ) hai
